CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 24, 1962, pg. 6 reads: "To UN Meet - Shown preparing for their trip to the United Nations Assembly in Harrisburg, March 2 and 3, are, left to right: Mrs. Thelma Lovette; Andrea Williams and Nadine Woodward, who are club adviser and president, respectively, of the Sequoires Tri-Hi-Y of then Centre Avenue YMCA. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Thelma Lovette, Andrea Williams, and Nadine Woodward, gathered at table for Sequoires Tri Hi-Y Club meeting in Centre Avenue YMCA
